{"word":"H8350 - שָׁשַׁר - shâshar - shaw-shar' - Vermillion - வெர்மில்லியன்","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>שָׁשַׁר"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>shâshar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>shaw-shar'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Vermillion / வெர்மில்லியன்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"சிகப்புநிறம், ஜாதிலிங்கம் - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"redcolor, vermilion; formerly gained from `kermes' insect"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Perhaps from the base of <a href=\"#/H8324 - שָׁרַר - shârar - shaw-rar'/8324\">H8324</a> in the sense of that of <a href=\"#/H8320 - שָׂרֻק - sâruq - saw-rook'/8320\">H8320</a>; <i>red</i> ochre (from its <i>piercing</i> color): - vermillion."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H8338 - שָׁשָׁא - shâshâʼ - shaw-shaw'/8338\">H8338</a>, <a href=\"#/H8339 - שֵׁשְׁבַּצַּר - Shêshᵉbatstsar - shaysh-bats-tsar'/8339\">H8339</a>, <a href=\"#/H8343 - שָׁשַׁי - Shâshay - shaw-shah'-ee/8343\">H8343</a>, <a href=\"#/H8344 - שֵׁשַׁי - Shêshay - shay-shah'-ee/8344\">H8344</a>, <a href=\"#/H8347 - שֵׁשַׁךְ - Shêshak - shay-shak'/8347\">H8347</a>, <a href=\"#/H8348 - שֵׁשָׁן - Shêshân - shay-shawn'/8348\">H8348</a>, <a href=\"#/H8349 - שָׁשַׁק - Shâshaq - shaw-shak'/8349\">H8349</a>, <a href=\"#/H8350 - שָׁשַׁר - shâshar - shaw-shar'/8350\">H8350</a>"}]}